snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Security Breach - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Five Nights at Freddy's: Security Breach is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/five-nights-at-freddys-security-breach-switch/

In Five Nights at Freddy’s: Security Breach, play as Gregory, a young boy who’s been trapped overnight inside of Freddy Fazbear’s Mega Pizzaplex. With the help of Freddy himself, Gregory must uncover the secrets of the Pizzaplex, learn the truth, and survive until dawn.

#FiveNightsatFreddys #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
